I added a detailed technical comment to the forum topic confirming the root cause (missing `--print` flag causes TUI mode which doesn't produce line-delimited stdout) and providing specific guidance on the fix:
- Use `--print --input-format stream-json --output-format stream-json` for proper programmatic I/O
- Parse JSON in `_read_stdout()` instead of plain text lines
- Format user messages as JSON in `send()`
- Add `--permission-mode bypassPermissions` for headless operation

